 and develops alternative energy technologies it provides a full range of services for handling organic residuals in a period where innovation and sustainability are paramount the firms technology solutions include anaerobic digestion and mixed waste plastics to diesel it uses process source separated organics in anerobic digestors to divert from landfills and recover biogas this biogas can be converted to gaseous fuel for industrial processes electricity to the grid and cleaned for compressed renewable gas the company was founded by gerald p hamaliuk and marc m hazout and is headquartered in toronto canada website httpwwwsusglobalenergycom in the news see more sec june   susglobal energy canada corp filed form q relsci june   ryan duffy is now serving in a new board position at susglobal energy canada corp relsci june   laurence w zeifman is now serving in a new board position at susglobal energy canada corp executives  employees gerald p hamaliuk chief executive officer  director marc m hazout chairman  president board of directors marc m hazout founder at silver dragon resources inc laurence w zeifman independent member board of directors at susglobal energy canada corp gerald p hamaliuk chief executive officer  director at susglobal energy canada corp ryan duffy former president  chief executive officer at blackstone energy services inc see our list of current and previous board members when you upgrade start my free trial ➤ see more paths to susglobal energy canada corp susglobal energy canada corp you connections via relationship science susglobal energy canada corp sync your contacts to see how you can connect with susglobal energy canada corp start my free trial ➤ see more youve reached your  free profiles limit this month upgrade to relsci pro today to enjoy unlimited article views and much more start my free trial ➤ still not convinced check out our full listing of features here are you a relsci pro subscriber login to relsci pro  ➤ not a pro subscriber lo